short_description:
LockmyDrive is a portable data security software that offers a quick, easy in use and reliable protection of private files and folders on internal and external hard drives, USB Flash drives, memory cards. 

LockmyDrive allows you to:
- Lock your storage drive with a password restricting access to its contents;
- Hide all or some of your private files and folders making them invisible and inaccessible to others;
- Encrypt your files and folders using enhanced encryption technology;
- Keep your files safe in a secure online file storage.

With LockmyDrive you can be sure that nobody will see, copy or delete your private files. You can use  LockmyDrive at home, office or while traveling to protect your private data from prying eyes, unwanted intrusions, hackers, data thieves or computer viruses.
